collection.description: Kittens Against Cancer is an NFT collection generated to support cancer treatment and research.  It will consist of 15,000 unique Kitten NFTs, with no two the same.  A 100% of the proceeds of the initial sale (less taxes and fees) will go to cancer charities.  Further 50% of royalties from future resales will similarly be donated to support cancer treatment and research.  Hopefully, this will help to inspire people and use this platform to serve the greater good while supporting art.  Expecting an Early-Mid September Launch.  Ultimately it would be great if $1,000,000 could be raised in support of Cancer Charities, an issue that strikes close to home for me and I am sure many others.
